{"tid":2106319,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中国暴雨3789萬人次受災，141人死亡或失蹤，倒塌房屋2.8萬間","createTime":"2020-07-13T09:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T09:49:00.000Z","uid":293677,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"aa47b7db0bc39817a543af992b4e1576d5865171","tid":2106319,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:09:07.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cgqme4z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcgqme4z.jpg&h=8bae073a&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3226506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3226506&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxK0J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=578beb54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3226506&h=93fa8a1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3226506</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020-07-13 12:04:49<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕由於近日中國長江中下游發生洪災，今日上午國務院政策例行記者會也圍繞著防洪相關議題，中國水利部副部長葉建春在會中表示，已有33條河川發生超過歷史紀錄的洪水。<br />\n<br />\n葉建春指出，6月以來中國共有433條河川超越警戒水位，其中109條河川超過「保證水位」（最高防洪水位），33條河流則發生超過歷史紀錄的洪水，長江、黃河上游、珠江流域西江和北江、太湖等先後發生洪水，且目前洞庭湖、鄱陽湖和太湖水位仍處於超越警戒狀態。葉建春強調，目前長江、太湖流域防汛形勢嚴峻。<br />\n<br />\n應急管理部副部長鄭國光在記者會中提到，目前洪災主要集中在長江和太湖流域，部分省區中小水庫、中小河流堤防發生險情，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">累計已緊急轉移224.6萬人次，有27省（區、市），3789萬人次受災，已有141人死亡或失蹤，倒塌房屋達2.8萬間。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3226741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3226741&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxK0J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=7fbaa6cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3226741&h=b665b56e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3226741</a><br />\n<br />\n2020-07-13 15:25:32<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國南方連日暴雨成災，長江中下游災情慘重，累計已有27省（區、市）3789萬人次受災、2.8萬間房屋倒塌，已有33條河川發生超過歷史紀錄的洪水，<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"xx-large\">因降雨帶往北移，中國水利部副部長葉建春表示，未來「北方河流可能發生區域性較大洪水」。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，葉建春今在國務院政策例行記者會中表示，入汛以來，中國共有433條河川超越警戒水位，其中109條河川超過最高防洪水位，33條河流則發生超過歷史紀錄的洪水，目前洞庭湖、鄱陽湖和太湖水位仍處於超越警戒狀態，強調長江、太湖流域防汛形勢嚴峻。此外，他也表示中國即將進入防汛關鍵期，降雨帶即將北移，預計北方河流可能發生區域性較大洪水。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">中國中央氣象台今日預測，16日之前，長江中下游等地降雨持續，長江九江段水位持續超出警戒，未來幾天鄱陽湖水位也將繼續上漲。但17至21日，雨帶東段北移，預測西北地區東南部、黃淮中南部、江漢、江淮、江南西北部、四川盆地東部及雲南中西部等地會有大雨到暴雨，局部地區將出現大暴雨。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">天譴係會繼續黎</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bf7440bb5bfbded00d0dca00958720c972c87b","tid":2106319,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36794dc49bdbe7a39598cdcf6d39db41f10f217","tid":2106319,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:13:18.000Z","msg":"沖走搵唔到條屍  唔計<br />\n因交通而失救  唔計<br />\n電死  唔計<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8384844942a1dead4dab856c8053b4e2eeca317f","tid":2106319,"uid":288670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"無理由 點會多過35人 係咪想犯黨安法"},{"pid":"3bd6e87727d798fabfb55c59e2f24f8b46a5cb95","tid":2106319,"uid":309398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cite